title: California Bans State Travel To Florida And 4 Other States
description: California added five more states, including Florida, to the list of places where state-funded travel is banned because of laws that discriminate against members of the LGBTQ community, the state attorney general announced Monday.

title: Venomous cobra on the loose in north Raleigh neighborhoodMiami condo collapse
description: The zebra cobra was last seen on Sandringham Drive in northwest Raleigh, according to a warning issued by police at 1:30 a.m. The neighborhood, called Brittany Woods, is near Leesville Road.
